  "text": "## Account Management  \n**Q: How do I check my balance?**\nA:\n- **Online Banking:** Log in to www.firstuk.bank\n- **Mobile App:** Open FirstUK Bank app\n- **Phone:** Call 0800-555-2265\n- **ATM:** Insert card and check balance\n- **Branch:** Ask teller  \n**Q: How do I access online banking?**\nA:\n1. Visit www.firstuk.bank/login\n2. Enter username and password\n3. Complete two-factor authentication (OTP via email/SMS)\n4. Access your account  \n**Q: Can I close my account anytime?**\nA: Yes. No penalties or notice required. To close:\n- Call 0800-555-2265\n- Visit a branch\n- Submit online form  \nYour final balance will be transferred (check, bank transfer, or cash).  \n**Q: What happens if my account becomes dormant?**\nA: If no activity for 12 months:\n- Account marked \"dormant\" (no impact on you)\n- Interest still earned\n- You can still deposit/withdraw\n- We'll send a letter to confirm status  \n---",
